<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>276</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa pakcha'n Hossana ti'n kiko un,
 Lawp takin Lalpa pak un;
 Lunggil kipaka Lalchutphah tun dingin,
 Amin thiengtho let sakun.
 A puonlap vannuoi a masawn zelin,
 A hehpihna muonga chieh zelin;
 A Pathien na I chung ah hung eng ina,
 A khutin ei pui zel intin, Tu leh kumsawt in.

[V2]
 Chawllo a chieh zelin, I chunga puonlap kipei tawh,
 Chawllo a chieh zelin, lawpna la chuh sa kawm zelin;
 Chawllo a chieh zelin, mei leh meipi'n I mau a pui hi,
 Chunglam a I kumsawt In lopi tung di'n.

[V3]
 2. Lalpa pakun, Amah kumsawt vaihawm pa,
 Chungnung pen ah lopi hen;
 Amin chuh pakcha'n A lungsiet na ziekin,
 Chung Van lapi sakpih un.
 Masawn zelin lung kiguol a chieh in,
 Isu nungzuite laka chieh in;
 Chawlhna In nuom lunggil lawpin zuon hitiu,
 A nunnuom te'n Hukdampa a pahchak nau mun ah.</lyrics>
<title>PRAISE YE THE LORD!</title>
</song>